{"tid":546511,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)國定殺戮日1-3","createTime":"2018-01-31T15:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T17:29:02.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"454a7324b3ac235bdf4b73c652f2c63aa975375e","tid":546511,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=J%2BGjt9OVN8jpNQuOpJCvz8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=86df0ade\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=J%2BGjt9OVN8jpNQuOpJCvz8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=10e04747\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/70/The_Purge_Election_Year_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F70%2FThe_Purge_Election_Year_Poster.jpg&h=86e08f60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/29/The_Purge_&ndash;_Anarchy_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F29%2FThe_Purge_%E2%80%93_Anarchy_Poster.jpg&h=eec245f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.2022年，殺戮日開始的兩小時前，商人詹姆士&middot;桑丁在自己的家庭保全裝置而使自己公司銷售額大獲全勝，於是開心地回到自己家向妻子瑪麗、女兒佐伊與兒子查理宣布了好消息，隨後與家人等待殺戮夜晚的來臨。兩小時後，殺戮日開始的一分鐘前，詹姆士野心勃勃地為家人展示了自己引以為豪的堡壘型保全系統：利用幾英尺高的淬火鋼封住所有的窗戶與大門，說明他們絕對可以高枕無憂。一分鐘後，美國電視開始播報預警系統，城市也隨著警報聲的響起開始了長達十二小時的大屠殺，而桑丁一家決定利用娛樂來打發接下來的幾個小時..<br />\n<br />\n2.2023年，在洛杉磯市區中，警察中士李歐&middot;巴恩斯在全副武裝、身穿防彈衣、不顧自己前妻的警告而開著一輛加固警車，打算利用這場夜晚去殺一個他最憎恨的人。夜幕降臨，全國開始播報預警系統，洛杉磯也隨之展開了了長達十二小時的大屠殺，虎視眈眈的人們開始手持武器、大呼痛快地走到街道上獵殺。不到兩個小時，洛杉磯變成了一片充滿黑暗、戰火、鮮血與屍體的「無政府天堂」！李歐開著車原本計畫開高速公路到達目的地速戰速決，卻發現高速公路上滿是燃燒的汽車而被迫掉頭開往了市區。在市區裏，一對年輕夫妻夏恩與麗茲因為汽車拋錨而被困在了街上，為了躲避一群神秘的面具團夥而一直奪命狂奔...<br />\n<br />\n3.一年前選擇寬恕弒子的男人後，前警長里歐&middot;巴恩斯（Leo Barnes）成為了參議員夏琳&middot;羅安（Charlene Roan）的保全隊長。夏琳因誓言消滅清除組織而在下屆總統選舉中一路領先，但在最後一波清洗的當晚，一位政府內部的叛徒迫使巴恩斯和羅安走上街頭為生存而戰..<br />\n<br />\n11 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=J%2BGjt9OVN8jpNQuOpJCvz8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=630e47d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=J%2BGjt9OVN8jpNQuOpJCvz8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d5373d6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10e01ceb91596705aab03df87b103792eae2c0e","tid":546511,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18200eca0cdf75fb19b074ebe33116dc5f414d9","tid":546511,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189db761b9a01eec3e8f56b78d4b71fb7018a971","tid":546511,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T16:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a39a87163f1872aa0d57dafb06c08bc75f17d4d","tid":546511,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}